name: Todo me pasa a mi
description:
Everything happens to me, I am in every baby who cries.

In every old man alone in his house, in every artist who does not sleep to finish his piece of work and in every child who runs happily in the park. 
I created an island all to myself and yet I didn't understand where all those people came from? Until I realized that we are all the same person...I created an island all to myself and yet I didn't understand where all those people came from? Until I realized that we are all the same person...
